#news-blog-event-content.container
    #top-link.visible-xs-block
        i.fa.fa-chevron-up
        br
        | Top
    .row
        header.col-xs-12
            #header-inner
                h1
                  | Mountain Information Network
                .blue-border
    .min-landing.row
      .min-landing--main-column
          p For real-time, location-specific information on riding conditions this winter!

          h3 How to GET information
          p Click on any of these symbols on our main map
          .min-landing--pins.row
            ul.col-md-6
              li 
                i.min-map-icon--quick
                span Quick Report
              li 
                i.min-map-icon--avalanche
                span Avalanche Report
              li 
                i.min-map-icon--snowpack
                span Snowpack Report
            ul.col-md-6
              li 
                i.min-map-icon--weather
                span Weather Report
              li 
                i.min-map-icon--incident
                span Incident Report
              li 
                .min-marker-cluster 
                  span 4
                span Multiple Clustered reports

          p Zoom in to separate into single reports

          h3 How to GIVE information

          .row
            .col-md-7
              p Learn how to create and view <strong>detailed</strong> reports<br/> on the website by watching the video below

            .col-md-5
              p Learn how to create and view <strong>quick</strong> reports on our smart phone app from the video below
          .row
            .play-video.col-md-7
              img(src="http://res.cloudinary.com/avalanche-ca/image/upload/h_250,c_fit/v1452808718/website/MIN-Mockup-Laptop.png")
              i.fa.fa-play-circle(ng-click="playDesktop()")

            .play-video.col-md-5
              img(src="http://res.cloudinary.com/avalanche-ca/image/upload/h_250,c_fit/v1452808718/website/MIN-Mockup-Phone.png")
              i.fa.fa-play-circle(ng-click="playMobile()")

          p
            | At this time, only the website offers full functionality in submitting and viewing all types of reports. 
            | The table below compares the features currently available on each platform.

